evidence.source_document: Verified Complaint and Ex Parte Application for TRO and PI, Notice of Exparte Application for TRO and PI for Injunctive Relief to Halt Implementation of San Rafael Code 19.50 and SMC 19.20.080(c) on August 16th 2023
evidence.text: A lawsuit has been filed against the City of San Rafael. A Complaint and concurrent Ex-Parte Motion for TRO and Preliminary Injunction and Attached Exhibits is being filed in the US District Court. A judge shall be assigned to this lawsuit and motion, and a hearing date set on PLAINTIFFS motion for TRO.
